Package: IMPACTncdEngland
Type: Package
Title: Simulation Framework for Public Health Impact Modeling in England
Version: 1.0.0
Date: 2026-01-10
Authors@R: 
    person("Chris", "Kypridemos", , "christodoulosk@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-0746-9229"))
Maintainer: Chris Kypridemos <christodoulosk@gmail.com>
Description: 
  A simulation framework for evaluating public health policies and interventions in England using 
  synthetic populations, disease progression models, and Monte Carlo methods. This package supports 
  scenario-based modelling and integrates data management, exposure simulation, and visualization tools 
  tailored to the IMPACTncd_Engl model.
